# Postgres migrations directory.
#
# Migrations are managed by node-pg-migrate. Create a new migration with:
#   npm run db:migrate:create -- short-name-of-change
#
# Migrations run against POSTGRES_URL_NON_POOLING (single connection,
# stable session) per node-pg-migrate.config.json. Phase 1 ships zero
# migrations — schema lands in Phase 2 alongside the first dual-write
# entity (notifications).
